# CodepathMail

## Overview

CodepathMail is a simple Android application that displays a scrollable list of emails using RecyclerView.
This project was built as part of the CodePath Android Development Lab to practice dynamic lists and UI layout.

---

## Features Completed

Required Features:

* User can scroll through a list of emails
* Each email displays:

  * Sender
  * Email title
  * Email summary
* RecyclerView used to efficiently display items
* Clicking an email shows a Toast message

Optional / Improvements:

* Improved layout spacing and formatting
* Click listener added to RecyclerView items

